snippet.title: Uncharted: The Nathan Drake Collection – Uncharted 1 PS3 vs. PS4 Remastered Graphics Comparison
snippet.description:
GameStar PCs | Gaming PCs & Notebooks: http://www.one.de/shop/index.php
We are on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/candylandGS
Uncharted: The Nathan Drake Collection hier kaufen: http://amzn.to/1QKXy8V
Best Uncharted Collection Let's Play (German): http://bit.ly/1N0KX3E

We compare the graphics of Uncharted 1 Drake's Fortune on PS3 with the remaster from the Uncharted The Nathan Drake Collection Version on PS4. The Uncharted Collection runs on 1080p and 60fps – it improves textures, faces, characters, lighting, shaders, details and more. The Nathan Drake Collection includes Uncharted 1 Drake's Fortune, Uncharted 2 Among Thieves and Uncharted 3 Drake's Deception.
------------------------
Wir vergleichen die Grafik von Uncharted 1 Drakes Schicksal auf PlayStation 3 mit der remastered Version Uncharted The Nathan Drake Collection auf PlayStation 4. Die Uncharted Collection läuft in 1080p und 60 fps – sie verbessert Texturen, Gesichter, charaktere, Beleuchtung, Shader, Details und mehr. Die Nathan Drake Collection beinhaltet Uncharted 1 Drakes Schicksal, Uncharted 2 Among Thieves und Uncharted 3 Drake's Deception.

Music:
Nate's Theme – Uncharted: Drake's Fortune OST
Grave Robbing – Uncharted: Drake's Fortune OST
El Goddamn Dorado – Uncharted: Drake's Fortune OST
